mapper.name: {{9.properties_value.Name[].plain_text}} - PCAIC: {{1.UID}}
mapper.message:
Dear {{9.properties_value.Name[].plain_text}},

This refers to your request for a Personal Comprehensive Assessment and Initial Consultation (PCAIC).

Please be advised that the fees have been discounted and authorized by Mr. Jojo Duque (RCIC), and is also creditable to any future immigration application that you pursue with our firm.

However, this agreement and offer will EXPIRE IN 5 DAYS FROM THE DATE OF THIS EMAIL.

You must secure the payment AND sign the agreement before we can start the process.
_________________________

PAYMENT OPTIONS PLEASE READ CAREFULLY

*** COST: $157.50 ***
_________________________

OPTION 1: eTransfer (email money transfer)

You or your family/friend inside Canada may secure the payments using eTransfer to:

Name: DSMACS Consulting Inc.
Email: dsmacsincfinance@gmail.com

Please send us a receipt and password immediately after the transaction.
_________________________

OPTION 2: Credit Card (Visa/Mastercard/American Express/PayPal)

Please reply directly to this email (dsmacsincfinance@gmail.com) and request to pay via Credit Card.

We will send you a link promptly.

There is a $25 CAD charge per every transaction from $1 CAD to $500 CAD.

There is an additional $25 CAD charge per every $500 CAD transaction after that.
_________________________

OPTION 3: Wire Transfer (bank-to-bank)
You may secure your payment by Wire Transfer transfer (international)

OR

You or your family/friend inside Canada may drop by to the nearest ScotiaBank to make the payment.

The following is our credentials:

Duque Immigration Services Inc.
Bank Name: Bank of Nova Scotia
Transit #: 60517
Bank #: 002
Acct #: 0107018
CCP#: 6050593098007
SWIFT Code: NOSCATT

Please send us a receipt immediately after the transaction.
_________________________

Should you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us @ (204) 339-2522.

Best Regards,
Finance Team

Address: Unit 2 - 2536 Main Street, Winnipeg, MB R2V 4Y1
Phone: (204) 339-2522
Fax: (204) 339-2530
Facebook: @duqueimmigrationservices
Instagram: @duqueimmigration
